1. Network discovery scan:
   nmap -sn 192.168.240.132 0/24

2. Basic port scan:
   nmap 192.168.240.132

3. Service and version detection:
   nmap -sV 192.168.240.132
4. OS detection:
   sudo nmap -O 192.168.240.132

5. Vulnerability script scan:
   nmap --script vuln 192.168.240.132

6. Save output to file:
   nmap -sV -O 192.168.240.132 -oN nmap_full_scan.txt
